				Hey 👋, I'm Angel Suarez! 
				<a 
				    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/suarezangel/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
					class="flex items-center"
				>		
					<Badge>Disponible</Badge>
				</a>
			</h1>
			<h2 class="text-xl flex justify-center">
				<span class="text-amber-700/90">Desarrollador Full Stack.</span>
				<span class="w-2"></span>
				 De Argentina 💙🤍💙 🧉.
			</h2>
			<nav class="flex justify-center gap-x-4 mt-8">
				<Social herf="https://www.linkedin.com/in/suarezangel/">
					<LinkedIn class="w-6 h-6"/> 
					LinkedIn
				</Social>
				<Social herf="https://github.com/AngelBlackBlue">
